 Ability to initiate delay notification to applicant when we are at risk of missing, or have missed, a deadline. This is to stay in compliance with CPUC reporting requirements as specified in rulemaking 17-07-007, Decision 20-09-035, Section 5.1.6., Issue 12: Proposal 12e. Some current brainstorming ideas are to incorporate a button or link in the existing deadline-due email notifications.
